{{zh-hanzi|[[肥]][[水]][[不]][[落]][[外人]][[田]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: féi shuĭ bù luò wàirén tián
===Etymology===
Literally: Fertile water should not be placed in someone else's field.
===Proverb===
# An advantage should not be given to others.

